{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":865,"text":"Do you think it's possible\nto control someone's attention?"},{"time":5664,"text":"Even more than that,\nwhat about predicting human behavior?"},{"time":10157,"text":"I think those are interesting ideas."},{"time":12036,"text":"For me, that would be\nthe perfect superpower,"},{"time":14259,"text":"actually kind of an evil way\nof approaching it."},{"time":16616,"text":"But for myself, in the past,\nI've spent the last 20 years"},{"time":19743,"text":"studying human behavior\nfrom a rather unorthodox way:"},{"time":23245,"text":"picking pockets."},{"time":25201,"text":"When we think of misdirection,"},{"time":26741,"text":"we think of something\nas looking off to the side,"},{"time":29106,"text":"when actually the things\nright in front of us"},{"time":31355,"text":"are often the hardest to see,"},{"time":32978,"text":"the things that you look at every day\nthat you're blinded to."}]},{"cues":[{"time":35941,"text":"For example, how many of you still have\nyour cell phones on you right now?"},{"time":40671,"text":"Great. Double-check."},{"time":41912,"text":"Make sure you still have them."},{"time":43489,"text":"I was doing some shopping before."}]},{"cues":[{"time":45195,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":46274,"text":"You've looked at them a few times today,"},{"time":48216,"text":"but I'll ask you a question."},{"time":49590,"text":"Without looking at it directly yet,"},{"time":51467,"text":"can you remember the icon\nin the bottom right corner?"},{"time":55950,"text":"Bring them out, check and see\nhow accurate you were."},{"time":62382,"text":"How'd you do?"},{"time":63557,"text":"Show of hands. Did we get it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":66326,"text":"Now that you're done, close them down."},{"time":68184,"text":"Every phone has something in common."},{"time":69936,"text":"No matter how you organize the icons,"},{"time":71943,"text":"you still have a clock on the front."},{"time":73703,"text":"So, without looking at your phone,\nwhat time was it?"},{"time":77568,"text":"You just looked at your clock, right?"},{"time":79560,"text":"Interesting idea."},{"time":80735,"text":"Let's take that a step further\nwith a game of trust."},{"time":83203,"text":"Close your eyes."},{"time":84966,"text":"I realize I'm asking you to do\nthat while you just heard"},{"time":87632,"text":"there's a pickpocket in the room,\nbut close your eyes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":90655,"text":"Now, you've been watching me\nfor about 30 seconds."},{"time":94303,"text":"With your eyes closed, what am I wearing?"},{"time":97742,"text":"Make your best guess."},{"time":99163,"text":"What color is my shirt?\nWhat color is my tie?"},{"time":102671,"text":"Now open your eyes."},{"time":104046,"text":"Show of hands, were you right?"},{"time":106776,"text":"Interesting, isn't it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":107951,"text":"Some of us are a little bit\nmore perceptive than others, it seems."},{"time":111095,"text":"But I have a different theory\nabout that model of attention."},{"time":114055,"text":"They have fancy models of attention,\nPosner's trinity model of attention."},{"time":117614,"text":"For me, I like to think of it very\nsimple, like a surveillance system."},{"time":120972,"text":"It's kind of like you have\nall these fancy sensors,"},{"time":123763,"text":"and inside your brain\nis a little security guard."},{"time":126121,"text":"For me, I like to call him Frank."},{"time":128532,"text":"So Frank is sitting at a desk."},{"time":130512,"text":"He's got lots of cool\ninformation in front of him,"},{"time":132875,"text":"high-tech equipment, he's got cameras,"},{"time":134749,"text":"he's got a little phone\nthat he can pick up, listen to the ears,"},{"time":137879,"text":"all these senses, all these perceptions."},{"time":140354,"text":"But attention is what steers\nyour perceptions,"},{"time":142923,"text":"it's what controls your reality."},{"time":144717,"text":"It's the gateway to the mind."},{"time":146576,"text":"If you don't attend to something,\nyou can't be aware of it."},{"time":149411,"text":"But ironically, you can attend\nto something without being aware of it."},{"time":152922,"text":"For example, the cocktail effect:"},{"time":154588,"text":"You're in a party, having\nconversations with someone,"},{"time":157092,"text":"and yet you can recognize your name"},{"time":158799,"text":"without realizing\nyou were listening to that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":160976,"text":"Now, for my job, I have to play\nwith techniques to exploit this,"},{"time":164050,"text":"to play with your attention\nas a limited resource."},{"time":166919,"text":"So if I could control\nhow you spend your attention,"},{"time":170054,"text":"if I could maybe steal your attention\nthrough a distraction."},{"time":173087,"text":"Now, instead of doing it like misdirection"},{"time":175871,"text":"and throwing it off to the side,"},{"time":177419,"text":"instead, what I choose\nto focus on is Frank,"},{"time":179903,"text":"to be able to play with the Frank\ninside your head,"},{"time":182474,"text":"your security guard,"},{"time":183649,"text":"and get you, instead of focusing\non your external senses,"},{"time":186480,"text":"just to go internal for a second."}]},{"cues":[{"time":189365,"text":"So if I ask you to access\na memory, like, what is that?"},{"time":192575,"text":"What just happened? Do you have a wallet?"},{"time":194552,"text":"Do you have an American Express\nin your wallet?"},{"time":196815,"text":"And when I do that,\nyour Frank turns around."},{"time":199850,"text":"He accesses the file.\nHe has to rewind the tape."},{"time":202160,"text":"What's interesting is,\nhe can't rewind the tape"},{"time":204383,"text":"at the same time that he's trying\nto process new data."}]},{"cues":[{"time":207263,"text":"This sounds like a good theory,"},{"time":208789,"text":"but I could talk for a long time,\ntell you lots of things,"},{"time":211564,"text":"and a portion of them may be true,"},{"time":213294,"text":"but I think it's better if I tried\nto show that to you here live."},{"time":216378,"text":"If I come down, I'm going\nto do a bit of shopping."},{"time":218941,"text":"Just hold still where you are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":223503,"text":"Hello, how are you?\nIt's lovely to see you."},{"time":226211,"text":"Wonderful job onstage."},{"time":227386,"text":"Lovely watch, it doesn't\ncome off very well."},{"time":229474,"text":"Do you have a ring as well?"},{"time":230902,"text":"Good. Just taking inventory.\nYou're like a buffet."},{"time":233272,"text":"Hard to tell where to start,\nso many great things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235765,"text":"Hi, how are you? Good to see you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":237449,"text":"Hi, sir, could you stand up, please?\nJust right where you are."},{"time":240386,"text":"You're married,\nyou follow directions well."},{"time":242430,"text":"Nice to meet you, sir."},{"time":243604,"text":"You don't have a lot in your pockets.\nAnything down here?"},{"time":247288,"text":"Hopefully so. Have a seat. There you go.\nYou're doing well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":250082,"text":"Hi, sir, how are you?"},{"time":251566,"text":"Good to see you, sir.\nYou have a ring, a watch."},{"time":253795,"text":"Do you have a wallet on you? Joe: I don't."}]},{"cues":[{"time":255898,"text":"AR: Well, we'll find one for you.\nCome on up this way, Joe."},{"time":258703,"text":"Give Joe a round of applause.\nCome on up, Joe. Let's play a game."}]},{"cues":[{"time":261798,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":266437,"text":"AR: Pardon me."},{"time":268535,"text":"I don't think I need this clicker anymore."},{"time":270651,"text":"Thank you very much. I appreciate that."},{"time":272603,"text":"Come on up to the stage, Joe.\nLet's play a little game now."},{"time":275437,"text":"Anything in your front pockets?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":277132,"text":"J: Money."}]},{"cues":[{"time":278307,"text":"AR: Money! All right, let's try that."},{"time":280560,"text":"Can you stand right over this way for me?"},{"time":283352,"text":"Turn around and, let's see,"},{"time":284701,"text":"if I give you something\nthat belongs to me,"},{"time":286741,"text":"this is just something I have,"},{"time":288952,"text":"a poker chip."},{"time":290131,"text":"Hold out your hand for me."},{"time":292044,"text":"Watch it closely."},{"time":293218,"text":"This is a task for you to focus on."},{"time":295439,"text":"You have your money in your front pocket?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":297598,"text":"J: Yup.\nAR: Good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":298773,"text":"I won't put my hand in your pocket.\nI'm not ready for that kind of commitment."},{"time":302489,"text":"Once a guy had a hole in his pocket,"},{"time":304246,"text":"and that was rather traumatizing for me."},{"time":306183,"text":"I wanted his wallet,\nhe gave me his number."},{"time":308220,"text":"Big miscommunication."}]},{"cues":[{"time":309403,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":310428,"text":"Let's do this simply.\nSqueeze your hand tight."},{"time":312610,"text":"Do you feel the poker chip in your hand?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":314555,"text":"J: I do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":315729,"text":"AR: Would you be surprised\nif I took it? Say yes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":318052,"text":"J: Very.\nAR: Good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":319227,"text":"Open your hand. Thank you very much."},{"time":321034,"text":"I'll cheat if you give me a chance."},{"time":322758,"text":"Make it harder for me. Just use your hand."},{"time":324846,"text":"Grab my wrist, but squeeze, squeeze firm."},{"time":326841,"text":"Did you see it go? Joe: No."}]},{"cues":[{"time":329039,"text":"AR: No, it's not here. Open your hand."},{"time":330873,"text":"While we're focused on the hand,\nit's sitting on your shoulder."},{"time":335055,"text":"Go ahead and take it off."},{"time":336566,"text":"Now, let's try that again."},{"time":338038,"text":"Hold your hand out flat. Open it up."},{"time":339968,"text":"Put your hand up a little bit higher,\nbut watch it close."},{"time":342809,"text":"If I did it slowly,\nit'd be on your shoulder."}]},{"cues":[{"time":345983,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":347423,"text":"Joe, we're going to keep doing\nthis till you catch it."},{"time":350019,"text":"You'll get it eventually.\nI have faith in you."},{"time":352217,"text":"Squeeze firm.\nYou're human, you're not slow."},{"time":354331,"text":"It's back on your shoulder."},{"time":356241,"text":"You were focused on your hand, distracted."},{"time":358463,"text":"While you were watching,\nI couldn't get your watch off."},{"time":361353,"text":"Yet you had something inside your pocket."},{"time":363616,"text":"Do you remember what it was?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":365418,"text":"J: Money."}]},{"cues":[{"time":366593,"text":"AR: Check your pocket. Is it still there?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":368661,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":369686,"text":"Oh, there it was. Put it away."},{"time":371656,"text":"We're just shopping."},{"time":372831,"text":"This trick's more about the timing."},{"time":374543,"text":"I'm going to try to push it\ninside your hand."},{"time":376709,"text":"Put your other hand on top, would you?"},{"time":378903,"text":"It's amazingly obvious now, isn't it?"},{"time":380696,"text":"Looks a lot like the watch\nI was wearing, doesn't it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":383225,"text":"(Laughter) (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":384550,"text":"J: That's pretty good.\nAR: Oh, thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":386940,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":389226,"text":"But it's only a start.\nLet's try it a little bit differently."},{"time":392130,"text":"Hold your hands together.\nYour other hand on top."},{"time":394504,"text":"If you're watching this little token,"},{"time":396300,"text":"this obviously has become\na little target, like a red herring."},{"time":399272,"text":"If we watch this kind of close,\nit looks like it goes away."},{"time":402073,"text":"It's not back on your shoulder."},{"time":403673,"text":"It falls out of the air,\nlands right back in the hand."},{"time":406269,"text":"Did you see it go?"},{"time":408276,"text":"Yeah, funny. We've got a little guy.\nHe's union, works up there all day."},{"time":411694,"text":"If I do it slowly it goes straight away,\nit lands by your pocket."},{"time":414869,"text":"Is it in this pocket, sir?"},{"time":416146,"text":"Don't reach in your pocket.\nThat's a different show."}]},{"cues":[{"time":418623,"text":"(Squeaking)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":419717,"text":"That's rather strange.\nThey have shots for that."},{"time":422085,"text":"Can I show them? Rather bizarre.\nIs this yours, sir?"},{"time":424600,"text":"I have no idea how that works.\nWe'll send that over there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":427677,"text":"I need help with this one."},{"time":429074,"text":"Step over this way for me."},{"time":430367,"text":"Don't run away. You had something\ndown by your pants pocket."},{"time":433239,"text":"I was checking mine.\nI couldn't find everything,"},{"time":435516,"text":"but I noticed you had something here."},{"time":437314,"text":"Can I feel the outside for a moment?"},{"time":439212,"text":"Down here I noticed this.\nIs this something of yours, sir?"},{"time":442450,"text":"I have no idea. That's a shrimp."}]},{"cues":[{"time":444034,"text":"J: Yeah. I'm saving it for later."}]},{"cues":[{"time":446160,"text":"AR: You've entertained\nall of these people in a wonderful way,"},{"time":449208,"text":"better than you know."},{"time":450382,"text":"So we'd love to give you this\nlovely watch as a gift."}]},{"cues":[{"time":453425,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":454450,"text":"Hopefully it matches his taste."},{"time":455972,"text":"We have a couple of other things,"},{"time":457659,"text":"a little bit of cash."},{"time":459373,"text":"And we have a few other things,"},{"time":460882,"text":"these all belong to you,"},{"time":462072,"text":"along with a big round of applause\nfrom all your friends."}]},{"cues":[{"time":464774,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":465805,"text":"Joe, thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":467035,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":471913,"text":"(Applause ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":473934,"text":"So, same question I asked you before,"},{"time":476608,"text":"but this time you don't have\nto close your eyes."},{"time":479866,"text":"What am I wearing?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":481611,"text":"Audience: Oh!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":482786,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":484739,"text":"(Hesitant applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":489522,"text":"(Applause ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":490974,"text":"Attention is a powerful thing."},{"time":492899,"text":"Like I said, it shapes your reality."},{"time":495860,"text":"So, I guess I'd like to pose\nthat question to you."},{"time":498319,"text":"If you could control somebody's attention,"},{"time":500485,"text":"what would you do with it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":502600,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":503783,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}